his father and his brother

108
00:10:29,176 --> 00:10:31,336
He finishes by saying goodbye.

109
00:10:31,456 --> 00:10:34,616
But how is he getting by?
Has he got money?

110
00:10:43,616 --> 00:10:44,856
Iraqi dinars.

111
00:10:45,096 --> 00:10:48,176
How's he getting on in jail?

112
00:10:50,336 --> 00:10:51,976
I'm sure he's fine...

113
00:10:58,096 --> 00:10:58,936
