123
00:12:53,616 --> 00:12:54,856
Young man!

124
00:12:57,616 --> 00:12:59,856
- Are you OK?
- Yes, thank you.

125
00:13:01,656 --> 00:13:06,216
Do you know where I can find
the shepherd boys?

126
00:13:06,336 --> 00:13:09,376
